01:48.490 --> 01:50.226
What's wrong, Michael?

01:50.276 --> 01:52.867
Did you... see something?

01:52.977 --> 01:55.202
Uh, I-I see a kid who's
gonna make me late for prom, man.

01:55.252 --> 01:56.458
Come on, I got to get out of here, punk.

01:56.508 --> 01:57.936
I got to get showered
and get this tux on

01:57.986 --> 01:59.839
before the limo gets here.

02:13.392 --> 02:14.526
Come on, guys.

02:14.576 --> 02:15.976
We're supposed to hit the
trail in a half hour.

02:16.026 --> 02:17.485
- What are you doing?
- We're not going anywhere

02:17.535 --> 02:18.514
till we get some answers.

02:18.564 --> 02:19.615
About what?

02:19.665 --> 02:20.683
Last night.

02:20.733 --> 02:22.739
Yeah, where'd you and Deb disappear to?

02:22.789 --> 02:23.895
Seriously?

02:23.945 --> 02:25.835
She, uh, bring that
creepy mask with her?

02:25.885 --> 02:27.423
We were worried about you.

02:27.473 --> 02:28.642
Some of us.

02:28.692 --> 02:29.735
That mask isn't even hers.

02:29.785 --> 02:31.952
Okay, you guys have
the wrong idea about Deb.

02:32.746 --> 02:35.644
Yo, man. You totally banged her!

02:35.694 --> 02:37.481
What?

02:38.104 --> 02:39.896
No, I didn't.
-Yeah, you did.

02:40.015 --> 02:41.902
And I know you got it on that camera.

02:41.952 --> 02:43.307
Come on, let me check it out.

02:43.357 --> 02:44.931
Come on, let me check it out.

02:44.981 --> 02:46.388
- You guys are crazy!
- Come on, Joel!

02:46.438 --> 02:48.743
You're the one who had sex
with someone twice your age.

02:48.793 --> 02:51.107
We want details... now.

02:51.297 --> 02:53.922
Well, you and Drew got
pretty serious at the masquerade.

02:53.972 --> 02:56.154
Why don't you give us
some of those details?

02:56.612 --> 02:57.529
And on that note...

02:57.579 --> 02:59.518
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

03:00.135 --> 03:01.812
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

